SUNDAY WITH SANTA!
Santa is coming to Tomoka Outpost!
The real Santa will be back again this year in December 2024!
Times and details will come as soon as possible.
This is a very unique opportunity to get a picture with you and your family, friends or anyone you want to have with you in a picture with Santa.  The Tomoka River in the backdrop, convenience of the Tomoka Outpost and a wonderful day inside Tomoka State Park.  We are lucky enough to get the real deal, Santa himself here for your enjoyment so don't be late and get your festive holiday outfits ready!
Tomoka Outpost has some AMAZING event options!
Tomoka State Park has nearly 2,000 acres of fun, natural and unique outdoor opportunities for your events.
Give the Tomoka Outpost a call to talk details about your birthday party, wedding, corporate function, fundraisers, family reunion, high school reunion, celebration of life or any type of gathering you'd like...we've got what you need to make a lifelong memory!
*Our most popular event offering is our Riverside Patio.  We rent it in 3 section/options.  Give us a call for details!
If we don't have it already, we'll do what we can to try to make it the right fit for you and yours..
Just give us a call at 386-673-0022, ask for Capt. Scott and lets talk details/budget!
